snippet.title: Warner Bro. Is Flipping Out About The Depp—Heard Case
snippet.description: Amber Heard, a soy and toxic 3rd wave feminazi, lied and destroyed the career and subsequent life of Johnny Depp, one of the best and most accomplished actors of the 20th/21st century. As a fighter in the culture war, I’m a proud supporter of Depp who has lost almost everything because of apparent false allegations. Will Warner Bros., a company Against the dictator company Disney, think with logic or act in ignorance?
